no_trained_data %>% 
  filter(!estimate_sev == "NA") %>% 
  filter(!actual_sev == "NA") %>%
  mutate(error = estimate_sev - actual_sev) %>% 
  group_by(aid) %>% 
  summarise(mean(error),

Plot ERROR (svg)

error_plot_SVG = no_trained_data  %>% 
  mutate(aid = fct_relevel(aid, "Unaided","Aided")) %>%
  ggplot(aes(actual_sev, estimate_sev-actual_sev, color = aid))+
  geom_point(width = 0.1, size = 3, alpha = 0.5, shape = 16, color  ="gray80")+
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, color ="black", linetype = "dashed", size = 1)+
  geom_smooth(se = F, method = "loess", color = "red", size = 1.58)+
  facet_wrap(~aid)+
  xlim(0,75)+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(0, 75, by = 25)) +
  scale_color_colorblind()+
  #theme_half_open(font_size = 10)+
  theme_tidybayes() +
  labs(title = "",
       x = "Actual severity (%)",
       y = "Absolute error")+
    theme(legend.position = "none",
        strip.background = element_blank(),
        strip.text = element_text(size = 18, color ="gray5"),
    plot.title = element_text(size = 20), 
    axis.title.x = element_text(size = 16), 
    axis.title.y = element_text(size = 16),
    axis.text.x = element_text(size = 14)
        )

plot_LCCC_SVG = as.data.frame(em_ccc1_df) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(aid, emmean, color = aid)) +

             aes(aid, LCCC, fill = aid),
             position = position_jitterdodge(jitter.width = 0.07, dodge.width = 0.3),

             size = 2) +

                position = position_dodge(width = .4),
                width = 0,
                size = 1) +

            position = position_dodge(width = 0.6),

            show.legend = FALSE) +

gain_accuracy_SVG = no_train_ccc %>% 
  dplyr::select(rater, aid_training, LCCC) %>% 
  pivot_wider(values_from = LCCC,
              names_from = aid_training) %>% 
  mutate(slope1 =`Aided-no_trained`- `Unaided-no_trained`) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(`Unaided-no_trained`,slope1,label = rater ))+
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0, color = "red")+
  geom_point(width = 4, size = 3, shape = 16, color  ="gray50")+
